model

Interface Actions

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CircleElement, ComplexElement, Element, GeDocument, GraphicElement, ImageElement, Page, Project, RectangleElement, Slot, SoundElement, TextElement, VideoElement, Workspace

    public interface Actions
    This interface represents all the actions that can happen on the model.
    Those actions are: Inserting, Renaming, Deleting, Saving, Unbinding, Changing workspace, Sharing.
    Author:
    Dejan Radmanovic

    • Method Detail

      • addChild

        default void addChild(MutableTreeNode node,
                      String name,
                      Observer... o)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        General purpose of method is to insert another child which exists or is it yet to be created
        Parameters:
        node - MuatbleTreeeNode this parameter is used when you want to insert already existing child into the other node,
        or pass NULL if you want to create a new one
        name - String, this parameter is used when you want to assign a name to the objec, or if you want name to be auto genereted pass null.
        o - Observer..., this parameter is an array of indefinite size of observers that will be assigned to the node

      • rename

        default void rename(String newName)
        This method is Overridable later on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty
        Purpose of the method is, as its name suggests, to rename the node which implements Actions Interface
        Parameters:
        newName - an String of a new name that will be set.

      • delete

        default void delete(DeleteType deleteType,
                    ArrayList<MutableTreeNode> references)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        General purpose of method is to delete the node which implements this interface with different type of deletion.
        Parameters:
        deleteType - an ENUM of different types of deletion.
        references - an ArrayList of MutableTreeNode is a list of all shared nodes references used for delete all type.
        See Also:
        DeleteType

      • unbind

        default void unbind(ArrayList<MutableTreeNode> references)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        Purpose of method is to Unbind the node or "Let it lose" (Let it free with no parent). When you want to delete the node, but not completely just save it to draft
        Parameters:
        references - an ArrayList of MutableTreeNode is a list of multiple references if you want to unbind multiple references at once.

      • save

        default void save(String path)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        General Purpose of this method is to save node to the specified path and serialize component.
        Parameters:
        path - String of a path where that node will be serialized (Saved).

      • importChild

        default void importChild(String path,
                         Observer... o)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        Purpose of the method is to import already serialized, saved, Node from the specified path and assign an observers to it.
        Parameters:
        path - String of a path where is node serialized(Saved).
        o - Observer..., this parameter is an array of indefinite size of observers that will be assigned to the node

      • changeWorkspace

        default Workspace changeWorkspace(String pathToNewWorkspace)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        General purpose of the method is to load workspace from the specified path and return a instance of loaded Workspace.
        Parameters:
        pathToNewWorkspace - String of the path to the workspace that will be loaded.

      • share

        default void share(MutableTreeNode anotherParrent,
                   Observer... o)
        This method is Overrideable latter on by the class which implements Actions interface or be left default which is empty.
        Purpose of method is to share the action with another parent, or create shortcut of the current action to the Another parent action.
